The paper discusses the state-of-the-art of autonomous manufacturing systems, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The challenge also involved tasks such as object detection and force control, which are common topics in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and computer vision (cs.CV). The survey conducted among the teams also involved investigating the teams' strategies and approaches, which could fall under machine learning (cs.LG) and systems and control (cs.SY).
